cloud formation

Benfits:
infrastrcture as code
 * no resource manually created
 * the code can be version controll for git
 * changes to infra are reviewd through code
 
 
 cloudformation vs ansible vs terraform
 
 aws native is cloudformation will get latest updates
 ansible and terraform have to be updated every time a new services or api option comes from aws, which can take a long time
 
